latestPosts.caption:
From taking on oath to giving away the President batch, these 6 months went by in a blink of an eye!🥹

I became a member of this platform with a purpose and while I was entirely oblivious to the opportunities that it could offer in so little time, I was offered to become a President of an 8 year old chapter with 46 different Entrepreneurs! 

My thought during the oath? “I am the youngest one in this chapter, how will I manage the entire group?” “Everybody here is very familiar with each other, how am I going to put my point?” “Being a president is going to consume a lot of my time, how will I manage my own clients?” 

But you know, once we started with the leadership team, it was just as easy! 

I still remember how every Tuesday, I used to sleep at 2-2:30 in the morning after preparing my speech that I was supposed to deliver every Wednesday morning before the members & the MAJOR ups & downs that we, as a leadership team went through! 

It was a roller coaster ride but I was certain of what it is going to bring out of me💯

Here’s to 6 months of scratching our heads but enjoying every situation that we have been put through & an experience of a lifetime🥳

LT17
President
Create • Climb • Conquer
Oct 24’ to Mar 25’
